 Legend of Lee

 Beijing, April 10 (AP): Chinas national broadcaster has started filming a 40-part series on martial arts icon Bruce Lee, state media reported today.

 Xinhua said China Central Television started shooting The Legend of Bruce Lee over the weekend in Shunde in Guangdong province in southern China. Shunde is the ancestral home of Lee, who was born in San Francisco.

